    <item>
      <title>哈萨克斯坦民众称欧洲央行将讨论进一步降息但不确定性较高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/ecb-to-cut-rates-as-inflation-problem-nearly-solved-kazaks-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员马丁斯·卡扎克斯表示，欧洲央行下周很可能再次降息，尽管政策制定者将讨论比平时更大幅度的举措，但他们应该谨慎行事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/ecb-to-cut-rates-as-inflation-problem-nearly-solved-kazaks-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 06:30:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比跌至历史新低，债券在经济增长放缓后上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/rupee-falls-to-new-record-low-bonds-gain-after-growth-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示经济增长大幅放缓，印度卢比跌至历史新低。市场押注央行可能比预期更早降息，债券价格延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/rupee-falls-to-new-record-low-bonds-gain-after-growth-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 04:57:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
